items.title: Solano Public Health to host town hall-style meeting to discuss COVID-19 vaccine rollout and distribution
items.summary: Everyone is invited to join Solano County Public Health this Friday, January 22, 2021 starting at 3:30 p.m. via the Solano County Public Health Facebook page for a live town-hall style community meeting to discuss the COVID-19 vaccine rollout and distribution in Solano County.
